name: Butterflies on the cosmic garden
description: "These cyber butterflies get attracted by the radiation emitted from the plants that live in space. Only with Gama filters we can see the true colors of this radiosynthesis feast." || This is a digitally developed art originally painted on its negative colors on paper using watercolor technique. This limited edition of the reveled piece is 4178x3048 px, 12.5 MB, painted in 140lb cold pressed cotton paper (8.6x9 inches).
